	<h2>Backup of MySQL and MariaDB databases</h2>
	<p class="text">Iperius Backup is the most complete and reliable software to back up MySQL databases. It works with all versions of MySQL (5.x, 4.x, 3.23) and MariaDB, and has many powerful capabilities like compression, encryption, verification and restore. Iperius is extremely easy to use, and with a single license you can back up an unlimited number of servers and databases (local or remote), without needing any prerequisite.</p>
</div>
<div class="clearfix">
</div>
<div class="column" style="padding-top:50px; text-align:center;">
